.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vFNc5JK7LFF2FFu2iCPFb9-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vFNc5JK7LFF2FFu2iCPFb9-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vFNc5JK7LFF2FFu2iCPFb9-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vFNc5JK7LFF2FFu2iCPFb9-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vFNc5JK7LFF2FFu2iCPFb9-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vFNc5JK7LFF2FFu2iCPFb9-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vFNc5JK7LFF2FFu2iCPFb9-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vFNc5JK7LFF2FFu2iCPFb9.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vFNc5JK7LFF2FFu2iCPFb9.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: H\u0026amp;M Home)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eUnless you have a large \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/all-rooms/kitchen\" data-url=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/all-rooms/kitchen\" data-hl-processed=\"none\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"/all-rooms/kitchen\"\u003ekitchen\u003c/a\u003e with lots of storage or an equally substantial budget, investing in seasonal crockery might not be top of your agenda. What I love about these leaf plates is that they\u0026#39;re not overly seasonal - while the green colour works well for Spring themes, you can use these all year round when hosting or sprucing up a weeknight dinner.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-3utZcoetAZVCC83LWLXvFa\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt\u0026#39;s safe to say I have expensive taste when it comes to homeware so finding dupes of the brands and styles I love is crucial. I like to keep my 